Sheep pox and goat pox, Kyrgyzstan


Information received on 24/02/2012 from Dr Zhanybek Sultanov, Director General, State Veterinary Department, State Veterinary Department, BISHKEK, Kyrgyzstan

Summary
Report type Immediate notification
Start date 17/02/2012
Date of first confirmation of the event 24/02/2012
Report date 24/02/2012
